# 🎨 E-Commerce Frontend (React + Redux-Saga)

A modern e-commerce web frontend built with **React**, **Redux**, **Redux-Saga**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **Axios**.

---

## 📌 Tech Stack

- React 18+
- Redux Toolkit
- Redux-Saga
- React Router DOM 6+
- Axios
- Tailwind CSS

---

## 📦 Prerequisites

- **Node.js** ≥ 18.x
- **NPM** ≥ 9.x (or yarn)

---

## 📦 Project Setup

1️⃣ Install dependencies:
```bash
npm install
